<table><tr><td>Piersol CV, Jensen L. Occupational therapy practice guidelines for adults with Alzheimer's disease and related major neurocognitive disorders. Bethesda (MD): American Occupational Therapy Association, Inc. (AOTA); 2017. 45 p. [295 references]</td></tr></table>            </div>
